trans-unit.source:
Callers of this interface shall examine the return type in order to obtain a particular subinterface of BeanContextChild as follows: <code>
 BeanContextChild bcc = o.getBeanContextProxy();

 if (bcc instanceof BeanContext) {
      // ...
 }
 </code> or <code>
 BeanContextChild bcc = o.getBeanContextProxy();
 BeanContext      bc  = null;

 try {
     bc = (BeanContext)bcc;
 } catch (ClassCastException cce) {
     // cast failed, bcc is not an instanceof BeanContext
 }
 </code>
